<pb n="0056a" id="I01.0021.0056a" ed="I"/>
<lb ed="C I" n="0056a00"/><milestone n="1" unit="juan"/><head type="no">No. 21</head>
<lb ed="C I" n="0056a00"/><juan n="001" fun="open"><mulu n="001" type="卷"/><jhead><title>馬鳴寺根法師碑</title></jhead></juan>
<div2>
<lb ed="C I" n="0056a01"/><p id="pI01p0056a0101">馬鳴寺</p>
</div2>
<div2>
<lb ed="C I" n="0056b01"/><p id="pI01p0056b0101">魏故
<lb ed="C I" n="0056b02"/>根法
<lb ed="C I" n="0056b03"/>師之</p>
</div2>
<div2>
<lb ed="C I" n="0056c01"/><p id="pI01p0056c0101"><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">師</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">諱</unclear>□□□□□□<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">子</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">之</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">孫</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">也</unclear>。<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">法</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">師</unclear>□□□□□□<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">稟</unclear>。五緯□□□□□□<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">生</unclear>
<lb ed="C I" n="0056c02"/>□知□□□於齠歲。潔行與白<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">雪</unclear>爭光。溫<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">穆</unclear>與鮮雲<note n="0056001" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB15137;＝競【史】</note><app n="0056001"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">競</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB15137;</rdg></app><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">潤</unclear>。<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">爰</unclear>自弱年。英聲早集。
<lb ed="C I" n="0056c03"/>孝敬天然。<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">曾</unclear>閔無以喻其性。敏悟<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">冠</unclear>時。顏冉<note n="0056002" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30465;＝罕【史】</note><app n="0056002"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">罕</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30465;</rdg></app>得比其高。堯昂孤上。如長林之
<lb ed="C I" n="0056c04"/>出層雲。婉順迎襟。若清泉之入巨<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">壑</unclear>。湛〃然涇渭不能渾其津。灼〃乎<note n="0056003" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB00410;＝泥【史】</note><app n="0056003"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">泥</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB00410;</rdg></app><note n="0056004" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30466;＝滓【史】</note><app n="0056004"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">滓</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30466;</rdg></app>莫
<lb ed="C I" n="0056c05"/>能弊其輝。<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage"></unclear>岸崇峻。可聞而不可見。器韻堅廣。可<note n="0056005" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30467;＝鑽【史】</note><app n="0056005"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">鑽</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30467;</rdg></app>而不入。故使行逾素。德逾
<lb ed="C I" n="0056c06"/>深。志彌著。業彌遠。於是鸞舉<note n="0056006" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30468;＝拔【史】</note><app n="0056006"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">拔</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30468;</rdg></app>俗。<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">聳</unclear>慮法山之頂。鳳轉去塵。締誠滅影之域。識
<lb ed="C I" n="0056c07"/>火搆之弗康。了化城之休止。遂能<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">討</unclear>□三乘。<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">機</unclear>御十地。大夏閑居。授講後生。四
<lb ed="C I" n="0056c08"/>方慕義。雲會如至。雖鳩公之在<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">灞</unclear>西。未淂方其輻湊。朗上之在汶北。曷以加其
<lb ed="C I" n="0056c09"/>歸市。若夫八關之夜。立論之<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">際</unclear>。法師淵<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">瞻</unclear>凌發。風機獨遠。判沖<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">微</unclear>於百氏之中。
<lb ed="C I" n="0056c10"/>裁疑滯於一攬之內。理與妙共長。辭與玄同遠。興難則<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">眾</unclear><note n="0056007" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30469;＝席【史】</note><app n="0056007"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">席</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30469;</rdg></app>喪氣。復問則道俗
<lb ed="C I" n="0056c11"/>雷解。音清調逸。雅有義宗。<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">至</unclear>如課己追真。造次弗<note n="0056008" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30470;＝爽【史】</note><app n="0056008"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">爽</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30470;</rdg></app>。禪念求道。終生莫輟。割寶
<lb ed="C I" n="0056c12"/>營福。捨物如遺。造經數千。布滿繢素。刊建　聖顏。抽珍裁飾。祇洹妙<note n="0056009" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">穻＝宇【史】</note><app n="0056009"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">宇</lem><rdg wit="【原】">穻</rdg></app>。靡不瓖
<lb ed="C I" n="0056c13"/>麗。雖漢明寤寐金人。篾以過茲工也。方當虛器以導迷途。憑福以敷釋典。嘗不
<lb ed="C I" n="0056c14"/>憖遺。<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">忽</unclear>焉物化。春秋五十五。以正光四年歲次癸卯二月戊午朔三日庚申。殂
<lb ed="C I" n="0056c15"/>於寺。攸〃道俗。<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">莫</unclear>不悲悼。豈唯痛結師徒而已哉。粵翌日窆於含霞山之陰。法
<lb ed="C I" n="0056c16"/>師弟子三百人等。<unclear cert="low" reason="damage">並</unclear>聰慧一時。道器斯蔚。追匠誨之&CB07099;極。痛寒泉之方遠。綴徽
<lb ed="C I" n="0056c17"/>音於□□。□<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">道</unclear>聲於墳標。其辭曰。
<lb ed="C I" n="0056c18"/>昂藏<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">峻</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">緒</unclear>。渺<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">漫</unclear>長<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">灡</unclear>。繽紛組帶。蟬聯纓冠。或智或愚。能危能安。<note place="inline">其一</note>哲人云舉。&CB00048;
<lb ed="C I" n="0056c19"/>自<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">智</unclear>靈。<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">仰</unclear>□旻緯。府藉華涇。淵虯其志。雲鵠其聲。在素玉潤。<note n="0056010" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB20060;＝處【史】</note><app n="0056010"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">處</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB20060;</rdg></app>默金貞。去此火
<lb ed="C I" n="0056c20"/>宅。歸彼<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">化</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">城</unclear>。<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">玄</unclear>詞必討。妙理斯征。有有用曉。無無是磬。易和難<note n="0056011" resp="ihp" place="foot text" type="orig">&CB30471;＝染【史】</note><app n="0056011"><lem resp="ihp" wit="【史】">染</lem><rdg wit="【原】">&CB30471;</rdg></app>。載沖載盈。<note place="inline">其二</note>
<lb ed="C I" n="0056c21"/><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">浩</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">〃</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">精</unclear>□。□□深冰。辟諧法器。自何能稱。識非塵幕。悟是梵乘。飾相莊譯。珍麗
<lb ed="C I" n="0056c22"/>□□□□□□□<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">道</unclear><unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">徵</unclear>□□□□□□□□<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">憑</unclear>。<unclear cert="medium" reason="damage">刊</unclear>茲茂跡。不朽不凌。</p>
</div2>
</div1>
